<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Your virtual request #<%= @request.quote %> version <%= @virtual.version %> is ready</h2>
    <p>
      Attached are the virtuals you requested. Please let me know if you have any questions.
    </p>
    <p style="color: red">
      <strong>PLEASE NOTE: </strong>These proofs are general representations ONLY. All monitors and printers show different colors and are not accurate for viewing foils, printed inserts, or material colors. Virtuals are NOT considered camera-ready art or art department proofs.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks,</p>
    <p>
      <%= @request.artist.name %><br/>
      E: <%= @request.artist.email %><br/>
      P: <%= @request.artist.phone_number %><br/>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>